olor: red;\"><strong>（二） 從「誰才是暴徒」辯論陷阱脫身</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">港人對抗港府還算旗鼓相當，畢竟兩邊都是被法治洗禮過的香港人，但是港人對付中共的無底綫宣傳統戰技能，坦白說，還是太嫩。世人關心香港事態的焦點從「港人要自由、要自治」，變成「人民和政府誰才是暴力方」的辯論，這正是北京要製造的焦點轉移。</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">（三） 一切回歸三個字 &ndash; 真普選</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">核心訴求只有一個：真普選，一切口號、行動、宣傳，都環繞真普選這單一訴求展開，這樣，世界聽得懂，連中國內地人民都聽得懂。</span>"},{"pid":"427f3efc355e2999819621eaa447655b9eaef7c2","tid":1728190,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a467eb6c3d6e5215bd21c5cef3393f9961c7ceb0","tid":1728190,"uid":3302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cb6aa56c889637b012e845695f05c1585c6ad2af","tid":1728190,"uid":26353,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T18:33:51.000Z","msg":"搵工見到自己個post"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:36:49.000Z","msg":"中左 點算？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T16:16:14.000Z","msg":"先發制人"},{"pid":"c7a446f9902f60d7fafeb7d1d8701235e2df31f0","tid":1728190,"uid":226785,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T16:46:04.000Z","msg":"當面屌你"},{"pid":"ff98b13dca5fbda3be2c33c233d68b261645ceb2","tid":1728190,"uid":108236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T00:29:18.000Z","msg":"垃圾上司<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39752a404c5b4cce5aa21418d71c4c2cb934844e","tid":1728190,"uid":108236,"li